@NODE Voraus " Requirements"

	MEReset need OS2.0 or higher (min. OS3.0 to use Locale) and
	a AMIGA and nothing more.
	
	MEReset is only testet on a AMIGA 500 (OS3.0, 3 MB RAM,
	520 MB AT-HD).

@ENDNODE
	
@NODE Kann " What do MEReset??"

	MEReset is a small Commodity, which can reset your Computer
	(system confom!).

	MEReset have an small ARexx-Port (Name MERESET.REXX):

	 - Ende
		This cmd cancel the Program.

	 - Reset:
		This cmd reset your Computer, with the prg. parameters.

	 - QReset:
	 	resetet the Computer immediately (CAUTION!DANGER!).

	- Abbruch
	  	Cancel the CountDown.

	MEReset add now a item to the Tools-menu of the WB.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Bedienung " Using"

	I think it is very easy...

	Tooltypes:
	 SICHER - befor an Reset an Sure-Requester will popup.
	 ZEIT - the time for the CountDown.
	and the normal
	 CX_HOTKEY,CY_POPUP,CX_PRIORITY

	You can change this parameter also in the Prefswindow
	(Project->Prefs)

	The CLI/Shell-Version has only the Parameter ZEIT=,
	(for the Countdown) but the Countdown will not shown.
	(This comes in the next version).
	
@ENDNODE

@NODE install " Installation"

	You must only use the Install-Script to install the
	Program.

@ENDNODE


